{"tid":611824,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"［支那人柒事傳千里］三星以海報回應華為造假詆毀：S9+ 找不到 F/1.8 光圈！","createTime":"2018-03-31T12:02:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T06:55:40.000Z","uid":55951,"like":60,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"099b92ebf7131d31de8de25b07039ca483d15746","tid":611824,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:02:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/200039_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F200039_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5eec9a47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據悉，Samsung Galaxy 官方在微博發佈了一張廣告宣傳海報，從側面回應華為說法，聲稱 Galaxy S9+ 無論是日拍還是夜拍都很擅長，而且一貫如此。同時，Samsung 以嘲諷的方式指出了華為在 P20 Pro 發佈會中的一個明顯錯誤，即 Galaxy S9+ 根本沒有所謂的 F/1.8 光圈鏡頭。<br />\n<br />\nSamsung 官方在微博中表示，Galaxy S9+ 提供了 F/1.5 和 F/2.4 兩檔智能可變光圈，「在黑暗中發現光明，在強光中注目陰影」。而海報中Samsung回應華為稱，「對不起，在 S9+ 中無法查找到你搜索的 F/1.8 光圈。」 Samsung還強調，「其雙光圈模式可像人眼一樣自動適應強光及超低光環境。」<br />\n<br />\n此外，華為發佈會中，P20 Pro 的三鏡頭夜拍效果確實驚人，在與 Galaxy S9+ 的照片對比中技高一籌。但是，細心網友發現，華為 P20 Pro 是在 ISO 3200 感光度並且長曝光 30 秒才拍下的照片，而 Galaxy S9+ 長曝光竟然只持續了 10 秒。<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2018/03/31/samsung-response-to-huawei/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2Fsamsung-response-to-huawei%2F&d=y4chBs1IqmZRMRvYqKKP0JZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=a4293fac\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2018/03/31/samsung-response-to-huawei/</a><br />\n支那人究竟柒夠未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c43c71ec129822fe63f7679dfc3e371ec6c06c2","tid":611824,"uid":34793,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:17:09.000Z","msg":"發現支那好中意透過踩人去show off自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d09465058cfbcb34ba8c8fbc07b06932e74ec0","tid":611824,"uid":147376,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:21:01.000Z","msg"